@startuml
[*] --> WaitingForInput
WaitingForInput --> DisplayingCurrentTime : display current time
DisplayingCurrentTime --> ChoosingPowerLevel : choose power level
ChoosingPowerLevel --> SettingCookingTime : set cooking time
SettingCookingTime --> Cooking : start cooking
Cooking --> Inactive : door open during operation
Inactive --> WaitingForInput : return to waiting for input
Cooking --> Stopped : door opened during cooking process
Stopped --> WaitingForInput : return to waiting for input
WaitingForInput --> Cancelled : cancel cooking process
Cancelled --> WaitingForInput : return to waiting for input
@enduml
